.SH 8. TEXT AND STAMPS
\f[B]cpdf [\-stamp\-on | \-stamp\-under] stamp.pdf\f[R]
[\-scale\-stamp\-to\-fit] [] [\-relative\-to\-cropbox]
[\-process\-struct\-trees] \f[B]in.pdf\f[R] [] [\-fast] \f[B]\-o
out.pdf\f[R]
.PP
Stamp a one\-page PDF over or under each page in the given range.
