will be marked as an artifact.
.PP
\f[B]cpdf \f[R][\-add\-text <text\-format> | \-add\-rectangle <size>]**
[\-font <fontname>] [\-font\-size <size\-in\-points>] [\-load\-ttf
<name>=<file>] [\-embed\-std14] [\-color <color>] [\-line\-spacing
<number>] [\-outline] [\-linewidth <number>] [\-underneath]
[\-relative\-to\-cropbox] [\-prerotate] [\-no\-warn\-rotate] [\-bates
