%filename The full file name of the input document
%URL[text|URL] Add text, which links to URL (does not work for diagonal text)
%Bookmark<n> Bookmark text at level n (0, 1, 2, 3, 4)
%Bates bates number
.EE
.PP
And date and time formats:
